                <h2>The Roots of Tradition</h2>
                <p>Noor e Shifa was born from a deep respect for the healing power of nature. For generations, traditional herbal remedies have been the cornerstone of wellness in our culture.</p>
                <p>We believe that true healing doesn't come from a lab, but from the earth. Our journey started with a simple goal: to share these time-tested secrets with the modern world.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="image-content">
